  "texts": [
    "Prompt chainsA prompt chain is a sequence of prompts that computes a result step by step.",
    "Each step corresponds to the execution of an asset.",
    "Just like a prompt, a chain has inputs that can be parameters or non-textual data.",
    "The inputs of each step of the chain are either set to a constant value, a parameter of the chain or the output of a preceding step.",
    "Finally, the last step in the sequence computes the result, i.e., the output of the chain."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}